  "description": "Trefoil crossings at high tangle (0.7) act as gates — each of the 3 crossing points briefly redirects energy in the feedback matrix, creating a percussive gating effect at 2.5 Hz pulse rate. Square LFO1 hard-gates the filter at 2 Hz for additional rhythmic punctuation. Aggressive, punchy.",
